I"(<p>The <code>crimereports</code> sensor allows one to track reported incidents occurring in a given area. Incidents include anything reported to <a href="https://www.crimereports.com">Crime Reports</a>. Your regional emergency services may or may not report data. The sensor only counts incidents from the current day.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To enable this sensor, add the following lines to your <code>configuration.yaml</code>. Your <code>radius</code> should be of sufficient size to capture incidents in your area.</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">sensor:
  - platform: crimereports
    name: NAME_FOR_SENSOR
    radius: RADIUS
</code></pre>
<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
  <dl class=''><dt><a class='title-link' name='name' href='#name'></a> name</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>Custom name for the sensor.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='radius' href='#radius'></a> radius</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='float'>float</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>Radius in meters</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='latitude' href='#latitude'></a> latitude</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='float'>float</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Latitude for sensor.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>Your home zone latitude defined in your configuration.</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='longitude' href='#longitude'></a> longitude</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='float'>float</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Longitude for sensor.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>Your home zone longitude defined in your configuration.</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='include' href='#include'></a> include</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='list'>list</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>List of incident types to include. See below for a list of valid incidents.</p>
